export default () => `

About Me:

  • Education

    • I graduated from Penn State Beaver in 2006 with a BS in Psychology.

  • Life Experiences

    • I worked in adult Psychiatric Care for 5 years after I graduated. I chose to make a career change as a full-time Nanny, where I worked for 3 years. I am currently a stay at home mom that loves reading with her children.

  • Career Goals

    • The time I spent as a Nanny and a stay at home mom has taught me how important reading is to childhood development. It is for this reason that I chose to become a Consultant for Usborne. I hope to help more moms create this love of learning in their homes.

`;
